SHUTDOWN (Admin Command)
========================

Usage: shutdown

Initiate a graceful server shutdown.

This command will:
  1. Save all player data
  2. Disconnect all players with a shutdown message
  3. Stop the game loop
  4. Exit the server process

Notes:
  - Requires Admin access level
  - Cannot be undone once initiated
  - Players will need to reconnect after the server restarts

See also: promote
